posting_body: ['Ballard On the Park', '2233 NW 58th Street , Seattle, WA, 98107', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 32', 'OR Text', '32', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'Experience hygge at Home on the Park', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 669 - 1061 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'In a neighborhood historically called Little Scandinavia, Ballard on the Park embodies the Danish concept of deep contentment and cozy well-being—known as hygge—by blending an inviting, convivial atmosphere with the warm wood tones and clean lines of contemporary Scandinavian design.', 'Come home to a comfortable studio, one or two bedroom home that pairs an intuitive layout and modern features with access to resident amenities that enhance your relaxation and satisfaction.', 'Your journey begins here.', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $300 pet deposit per pet, and a $50 monthly pet rent.', 'Cats and dogs are allowed.', 'Other animals must remain in a cage.', 'Please call for complete pet policy information.', 'Other animals must remain in a cage.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Sunday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '5xzdnLXW']
